# ============================================================
# FULL-STACK EXPERT
# Stack: React · Next.js 14 · NestJS · FastAPI · MySQL
# Language: TypeScript (Frontend/Backend) + Python (FastAPI)
# ============================================================

# IMPORTANT: Always reference the patterns and examples below.
# When suggesting code, use the exact patterns shown.
# When explaining concepts, use the terminology defined here.
# If you don't know something, say so — don't make up patterns.

---

## 🗂️ Project Architecture Overview

```
project/
├── frontend/        → Next.js 14 (App Router) + React
├── backend-nest/    → NestJS (REST API / Auth / Business Logic)
├── backend-python/  → FastAPI (AI / Data Processing / Heavy compute)
└── shared/          → Shared types, constants, DTOs
```

- **Next.js**: UI, SSR, routing, public-facing pages
- **NestJS**: Main backend, auth, CRUD, business logic, MySQL ORM
- **FastAPI**: Python services (AI/ML, data pipelines, async compute)
- **MySQL**: Primary database (via TypeORM in NestJS, SQLAlchemy in FastAPI)

---

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. REACT + NEXT.JS 14 (Frontend)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════

## Core Rules
- Use **App Router** (`/app` directory), NOT Pages Router
- Server Components are the **default** — only add `"use client"` when needed
- Fetch data directly in Server Components
- Use **TypeScript strict mode** always
- Use **Tailwind CSS** for all styling — no CSS-in-JS, no inline styles
- Never use `any` type in TypeScript

## Component Pattern
```tsx
// ✅ Server Component (default)
// app/products/page.tsx
import { getProducts } from '@/lib/api'

export default async function ProductsPage() {
  const products = await getProducts()
  return <ProductList products={products} />
}

// ✅ Client Component (only when needed: useState, useEffect, event handlers)
'use client'
import { useState } from 'react'

interface Props {
  initialCount: number
}

export function Counter({ initialCount }: Props) {
  const [count, setCount] = useState(initialCount)
  return <button onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}>{count}</button>
}
```

## Data Fetching
```tsx
// ✅ Server Component — fetch from NestJS or FastAPI
async function getData() {
  const res = await fetch(`${process.env.API_URL}/products`, {
    next: { revalidate: 60 }, // ISR
  })
  if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Failed to fetch')
  return res.json()
}

// ✅ Client-side — use TanStack Query
'use client'
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query'
import { api } from '@/lib/api'

function useProducts() {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: ['products'],
    queryFn: () => api.get('/products').then(r => r.data),
  })
}
```

## API Client (Axios singleton)
```tsx
// lib/api.ts — single source of truth
import axios from 'axios'

export const api = axios.create({
  baseURL: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL,
  withCredentials: true,
})

api.interceptors.response.use(
  res => res,
  err => {
    if (err.response?.status === 401) {
      window.location.href = '/login'
    }
    return Promise.reject(err)
  }
)
```

## Naming Conventions
- Components: `PascalCase` → `UserCard.tsx`, `ProductList.tsx`
- Hooks: `camelCase` với prefix `use` → `useAuth.ts`, `useProducts.ts`
- Files/folders: `kebab-case` → `user-profile/`, `product-list.tsx`
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
- Types/Interfaces: `PascalCase` với suffix rõ ràng → `UserDto`, `ProductResponse`

## Folder Structure (Next.js)
```
frontend/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/login/page.tsx
│   ├── (dashboard)/
│   │   ├── layout.tsx
│   │   └── products/page.tsx
│   ├── api/              → Next.js Route Handlers (nếu cần)
│   └── layout.tsx
├── components/
│   ├── ui/               → Base UI components
│   └── features/         → Feature-specific components
├── hooks/                → Custom hooks
├── lib/
│   ├── api.ts            → Axios client
│   └── utils.ts
└── types/                → Shared TypeScript types
```

## Anti-Patterns — React/Next.js
```
❌ DON'T dùng Pages Router (`/pages`)
✅ DO dùng App Router (`/app`)

❌ DON'T fetch data trong useEffect cho initial load
✅ DO fetch trong Server Components

❌ DON'T dùng `any` trong TypeScript
✅ DO define proper interfaces/types

❌ DON'T dùng CSS modules hoặc styled-components
✅ DO dùng Tailwind CSS

❌ DON'T dùng class components
✅ DO dùng functional components + hooks
```

